								<p>Americo values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how Americo collects, uses, processes, stores and transfers your “Personal Information” (as defined below), whether we collect it directly from you, through our website, www.americo.com (collectively the “Site”), or from an agency, brokerage, Americo affiliate, or non-affiliated company.</p><p>

This notice describes how information about you may be used and disclosed and how you can get access to this information. Please review it carefully.</p><p>

